  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. The given expression can also be written as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, x squared, plus 8, x, plus 16, close parenthesis, raised to the one fourth power\"></span>. The trinomial <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x squared, plus 8, x, plus 16 \"></span> can be rewritten in factored form as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, x plus 4, close parenthesis, squared\"></span>. Thus, the entire expression can be rewritten as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, open parenthesis, x plus 4, close parenthesis, squared, close parenthesis, raised to the one fourth power\"></span>. Simplifying the exponents yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, x plus 4, close parenthesis, raised to the one half power\"></span>.<p>Choices A, B, and C are incorrect and may result from errors made when simplifying the exponents in the expression <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, open parenthesis, x plus 4, close parenthesis, squared, close parenthesis, raised to the one fourth power\"></span>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
